<h2 id="Configure-Access-Control-List-(ACL)" style=""><span id="EFSwitchConfigurationsforCXVoice-ConfigureAccessControlList(ACL)"></span>Configure Access Control List (ACL)
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.4/efswitch-configurations-for-cx-voice#Configure-Access-Control-List-(ACL)">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>For the Voice Connector to be able to access the EFSwitch ESL for communicating with EFSwitch, their IP address must be added to the ACL.</p>
<ul>
 <li>
  <p>Login to EFSwitch web interface.&nbsp;</p>
  <ul>
   <li>
    <p>Open in browser: <a href="https://ip-addr/" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer"><strong>https://IP-addr</strong></a>, where<strong> IP-addr</strong> is the IP address of the server that EFSwitch is deployed on.</p>
    <div class="theme-block-image">
     <image-lightbox>
      <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
       <img src="/__attachments/a_4769a85696ba65a66611b3688666c3993a626547cf3ba30979248a26ccc8494c/image2024-1-5_12-43-48.png?cb=e0fb4167248fcab330be378615bd194a" alt="image2024-1-5_12-43-48.png" data-scope="internal" width="787" height="707">
      </div>
     </image-lightbox>
    </div>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>Add the <strong>username</strong> and <strong>password</strong> that was shown upon <a href="/cx-knowledgebase/latest/media-server-deployment-guide" data-scope="internal">installation of EFSwitch</a> and press <strong>LOGIN</strong>.</p>
   </li>
  </ul>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Press the IP address in the top right and select the Domain created in the Domain creation section above:</p>
  <div class="theme-block-image">
   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_fc2ef814c074ef8d5ec7e6b77e0a8768c11fe5fe4e96d374e6b3affae1aea7c9/image2024-1-5_15-33-22.png?cb=ecdfbc098fd9c158692476a32a0e1c4e" alt="image2024-1-5_15-33-22.png" data-scope="internal" width="1280" height="372">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Open the <strong>Access Control List</strong> from the <strong>Advanced </strong>tab.</p>
  <div class="theme-block-image">
   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_6c6e8125e427f4cfce519c20c6d31af9f05b5bf24e1b0bd927203491dc2bca02/image2023-9-8_10-29-40.png%3Fversion=1&amp;modificationDate=1694150980542&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=450&amp;height=174?cb=a226c73c7ef2d20d6b1306b2e7dd603c" alt="image2023-9-8_10-29-40.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694150980542&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=450&amp;height=174" data-scope="internal" width="1013" height="392">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Create a new <strong>ACL </strong>with the <strong>Add </strong>button.</p>
  <div class="theme-block-image">
   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 600px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_0a61a9a56b88a439d4c08aa12c0d7374d0e26ca599edb07ff2883303bece9557/image2023-9-8_10-31-0-20240123-054415.png?cb=158ba2e7b4eaff172c4a0583edb99800" alt="image2023-9-8_10-31-0-20240123-054415.png" data-scope="internal" width="1741" height="390">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Set the name to <strong>esl</strong>,&nbsp; the <strong>Default </strong>to <strong>allow </strong>and add the following IP addresses:</p>
  <ul>
   <li>
    <p>127.0.0.1</p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>The IP address of the server the EFSwitch is running on e.g. 192.168.1.17.</p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>The IP address of the server the Voice connector is running on e.g. 192.168.1.201.</p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>Lastly, add the IP addresses of the docker container for the <strong>Voice connector</strong>.</p>
    <ul>
     <li>
      <p>On the Voice connector server, use the command <strong>docker ps </strong>to list the containers.</p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        <div class="theme-block-image">
         <image-lightbox>
          <div class="block-image" style="--width: 600px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
           <img src="/__attachments/a_ecabca0396b868f83076a71f1c6162aedb0c30e5caa3d2952170df2e56eef998/image2023-9-8_10-36-22.png%3Fversion=1&amp;modificationDate=1694151382954&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=51?cb=848aca959e3575fc6399c36361518ade" alt="image2023-9-8_10-36-22.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694151382954&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=51" data-scope="internal" width="1331" height="124">
          </div>
         </image-lightbox>
        </div>
       </li>
      </ul>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Run the command <strong>docker inspect containerID</strong> (where <strong>containerID</strong> is the container ID for the <strong>Voice connector</strong>) and scroll down to the Networks object and find the Gateway and IPAddress fields.</p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        <div class="theme-block-image">
         <image-lightbox>
          <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
           <img src="/__attachments/a_d37ddc64d0e191fcc8df6bcf7f647fe26d304596dd20236ed7bcf3ce42231cd2/image-20240123-054548.png?cb=635806abf91e291d5b0b28ddbb7e675d" alt="image-20240123-054548.png" data-scope="internal" width="404" height="361">
          </div>
         </image-lightbox>
        </div>
        <p>
         <br>
        </p>
       </li>
      </ul>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Copy these two addresses to the <strong>esl </strong>ACL.</p>
     </li>
    </ul>
   </li>
  </ul>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click the <strong>Save </strong>button and go to the <strong>SIP Status</strong> with from the <strong>Status </strong>tab.</p>
  <div class="theme-block-image">
   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_cbedf9a10cee0ff0edcbf67ce433bea398d4d9652e71ea95f50b623f0f6e92a8/image2023-9-8_10-42-31.png%3Fversion=1&amp;modificationDate=1694151751510&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=406&amp;height=250?cb=60d882aff2c52b3eccfc2a2ee9f7545a" alt="image2023-9-8_10-42-31.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694151751510&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=406&amp;height=250" data-scope="internal" width="929" height="571">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click the <strong>Reload ACL </strong>button on the top right.</p>
  <div class="theme-block-image">
   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 600px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_863a5b1bca8f51ee2f07226c1e64e838652fc60cacf7b328530a46134e92512e/image2023-9-8_10-43-23.png%3Fversion=1&amp;modificationDate=1694151803757&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=120?cb=4a346a7cb29131bb3279fc12d5e0516b" alt="image2023-9-8_10-43-23.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694151803757&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=120" data-scope="internal" width="1685" height="313">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
 </li>
</ul>
