   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_fc2ef814c074ef8d5ec7e6b77e0a8768c11fe5fe4e96d374e6b3affae1aea7c9/image2024-1-5_15-33-22.png?cb=ecdfbc098fd9c158692476a32a0e1c4e" alt="image2024-1-5_15-33-22.png" data-scope="internal" width="1280" height="372">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Open <strong>Settings </strong>from the <strong>Advanced </strong>tab.</p>
  <div class="theme-block-image">
   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_bb5180cbe40d0986ec9b67a2cf05f42013b3494f41cfb3d822a6b0853c34f754/image2023-9-7_10-58-23.png%3Fversion=1&amp;modificationDate=1694066302358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=187?cb=67714d790fe7c38c6a5b32b36d685d64" alt="image2023-9-7_10-58-23.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694066302358&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=187" data-scope="internal" width="1209" height="567">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Change the <strong>Event Socket IP Address </strong>to <strong>0.0.0.0</strong>, and the <strong>Event Socket ACL</strong> to <strong>esl</strong>.</p>
  <div class="theme-block-image">
   <image-lightbox>
    <div class="block-image" style="--width: 400px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
     <img src="/__attachments/a_8d0f848393e571a5b5d6fb27a90a4d131ba223e6b547b2c65e550bfebbce4aaf/image2023-9-7_10-59-24.png%3Fversion=1&amp;modificationDate=1694066363772&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=601&amp;height=250?cb=36bfb743f11d4abfb220c791c0971b2e" alt="image2023-9-7_10-59-24.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694066363772&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=601&amp;height=250" data-scope="internal" width="873" height="363">
    </div>
   </image-lightbox>
  </div>
  <ul>
   <li>
    <p>Optionally, change the <strong>Event Socket Password</strong> to the a different value, or leave as default <strong>ClueCon</strong>.</p>
    <ul>
     <li>
      <p>If the password is changed, then the same must be set in the environment file for the <a href="/cx/4.4/voice-connector-deployment-guide" data-scope="internal">voice connector</a>.</p>
     </li>
    </ul>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>If the password is changed, update it in the environment variables file of the Voice connector docker container.</p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>SSH into the Debian server onto which EFSwitch is installed.</p>
    <ul>
     <li>
      <p>Use command <em><strong>ssh username@server-ip</strong></em></p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Enter user password and press <strong>ENTER</strong>.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Use command <em><strong>su</strong></em>.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Enter root password and press <strong>ENTER</strong>.</p>
     </li>
    </ul>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>Run the command <strong>systemctl restart freeswitch</strong> to restart EFSwitch with the new ESL settings.</p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>Log out of EFSwitch in the browser and log back in.</p>
   </li>
  </ul>
 </li>
</ul>

